verses.text: \w It|strong="H3117"\w* \w is|strong="H3117"\w* good \w to|strong="H3117"\w* praise \w the|strong="H3117"\w* \w LORD|strong="H3068"\w*, \w and|strong="H3117"\w* \w to|strong="H3117"\w* \w sing|strong="H7892"\w* \w praises|strong="H7892"\w* \w to|strong="H3117"\w* \w Your|strong="H3117"\w* name, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* Most High,

\w For|strong="H5921"\w* \w You|strong="H5921"\w*, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* \w LORD|strong="H3068"\w*, \w have|strong="H5921"\w* made \w me|strong="H5921"\w* glad \w by|strong="H5921"\w* \w Your|strong="H5921"\w* deeds; \w I|strong="H5921"\w* sing \w for|strong="H5921"\w* \w joy|strong="H5921"\w* \w at|strong="H5921"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* \w works|strong="H5921"\w* \w of|strong="H5921"\w* \w Your|strong="H5921"\w* hands.

\w How|strong="H3588"\w* great \w are|strong="H3027"\w* \w Your|strong="H3068"\w* \w works|strong="H4639"\w*, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* \w LORD|strong="H3068"\w*, \w how|strong="H3588"\w* deep \w are|strong="H3027"\w* \w Your|strong="H3068"\w* thoughts!
\w A|strong="H3068"\w* senseless man \w does|strong="H4100"\w* not know, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* fool \w does|strong="H4100"\w* not understand,

\w that|strong="H3045"\w* though \w the|strong="H3045"\w* wicked sprout \w like|strong="H3808"\w* grass, \w and|strong="H3045"\w* \w all|strong="H3045"\w* evildoers flourish, \w they|strong="H3808"\w* \w will|strong="H3808"\w* \w be|strong="H3808"\w* forever destroyed.
\w But|strong="H7563"\w* \w You|strong="H3605"\w*, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* \w LORD|strong="H3068"\w*, \w are|strong="H7563"\w* exalted \w forever|strong="H5704"\w*!

\w For|strong="H3068"\w* surely \w Your|strong="H3068"\w* enemies, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* \w LORD|strong="H3068"\w*, surely \w Your|strong="H3068"\w* enemies \w will|strong="H3068"\w* perish; \w all|strong="H5769"\w* evildoers \w will|strong="H3068"\w* \w be|strong="H3068"\w* scattered.

\w But|strong="H3588"\w* \w You|strong="H3588"\w* \w have|strong="H3068"\w* exalted \w my|strong="H3605"\w* horn \w like|strong="H3068"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* wild ox; \w with|strong="H3068"\w* fine oil \w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w have|strong="H3068"\w* \w been|strong="H3605"\w* anointed.

\w My|strong="H7311"\w* eyes see \w the|strong="H7311"\w* downfall \w of|strong="H7161"\w* \w my|strong="H7311"\w* enemies; \w my|strong="H7311"\w* ears hear \w the|strong="H7311"\w* wailing \w of|strong="H7161"\w* \w my|strong="H7311"\w* wicked foes.\f + \fr 92:11 \ft Or my ears hear evildoers when they rise against me\f*

\w The|strong="H5921"\w* righteous \w will|strong="H5869"\w* flourish \w like|strong="H5921"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* palm tree, \w and|strong="H6965"\w* grow \w like|strong="H5921"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* cedar \w in|strong="H5921"\w* Lebanon.

Planted \w in|strong="H6662"\w* \w the|strong="H7685"\w* house \w of|strong="H6662"\w* \w the|strong="H7685"\w* \w LORD|strong="H3068"\w*, they \w will|strong="H6662"\w* \w flourish|strong="H6524"\w* \w in|strong="H6662"\w* \w the|strong="H7685"\w* courts \w of|strong="H6662"\w* our God.

\w In|strong="H3068"\w* old age \w they|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* still bear fruit; healthy \w and|strong="H3068"\w* green \w they|strong="H3068"\w* \w will|strong="H3068"\w* remain,

\w to|strong="H1961"\w* proclaim, “\w The|strong="H1961"\w* \w LORD|strong="H3068"\w* \w is|strong="H1961"\w* upright; He \w is|strong="H1961"\w* \w my|strong="H1961"\w* Rock, \w and|strong="H5750"\w* \w in|strong="H5750"\w* \w Him|strong="H1961"\w* \w there|strong="H1961"\w* \w is|strong="H1961"\w* \w no|strong="H1961"\w* unrighteousness.”
